Frequently-used unicode for quantum notation


https://github.com/j6k4m8/espanso-quantum

| Abbreviation | Expansion |
|--------------|-----------|
|<kbd>\\\\to</kbd> | ‚Üí |
|<kbd>\\\\bn</kbd> | ‚Ñï |
|<kbd>\\\\br</kbd> | ‚Ñù |
|<kbd>\\\\pi</kbd> | œÄ |
|<kbd>\\\\bb</kbd> | ùîπ |
|<kbd>\\\\cdot</kbd> | ‚ãÖ |
|<kbd>\\\\theta</kbd> | Œ∏ |
|<kbd>\\\\psi</kbd> | œà |
|<kbd>\\\\lambda</kbd> | Œª |
|<kbd>\\\\neg</kbd> | ¬¨ |
|<kbd>\\\\times</kbd> | √ó |
|<kbd>\\\\pm</kbd> | ¬± |
|<kbd>\\\\b1</kbd> | ùüô |

packageYml.name: package.yml
packageYml.content:
matches:
  - trigger: "\\\\to"
    replace: "‚Üí"
  - trigger: "\\\\bbN"
    replace: "‚Ñï"
  - trigger: "\\\\bbR"
    replace: "‚Ñù"
  - trigger: "\\\\pi"
    replace: "œÄ"
  - trigger: "\\\\bbB"
    replace: "ùîπ"
  - trigger: "\\\\cdot"
    replace: "‚ãÖ"
  - trigger: "\\\\theta"
    replace: "Œ∏"
  - trigger: "\\\\psi"
    replace: "œà"
  - trigger: "\\\\lambda"
    replace: "Œª"
  - trigger: "\\\\neg"
    replace: "¬¨"
  - trigger: "\\\\times"
    replace: "√ó"
  - trigger: "\\\\pm"
    replace: "¬±"
  - trigger: "\\\\bb1"
    replace: "ùüô"
  - trigger: "\\\\bra"
    replace: "‚ü®"
  - trigger: "\\\\ket"
    replace: "‚ü©"
